Description:
Hi! Are you looking for a **professional Figma UI UX website design**?

I'm a UI UX web designer with *5 years of experience* to help you.

**How does this gig work?**

Send all info for the project;

I'll create a custom offer for you to start with the website mockups in Figma.

**What can you expect from your web mockups:**

High conversion UI UX mockups in Figma;

Figma source file with the high quality, Pixel Perfect web design mockups which are ready for development;

Revisions and changes in the layout through your preferences;

Easy to navigate, intuitive, modern design mockups that make users press the "Call to Action" button in the simplest way ensuring Ui Ux;

Design that work, and help my clients to achieve their **business goals**.

**My background:**

378 completed designs: Marketplace, Ecommerce website; App design; One page website, Landing page; Dashboard; Business card;

**Niches:** software company, sales, business, online store, digital marketing agency, real estate, training, education, healthcare, beauty, restaurant, food, grocery, fashion, clothing brand, travel, portfolio, delivery, animals, pet, gaming, video, audio, fitness, repair services, tech

\*\*Feel free to contact me to get an offer\*\*

